sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 33: Agentic Sahayak V2 Tool-Calling Orchestration Sequence

  autonumber
  actor V as Vendor
  participant API as POST /api/ai/sahayak/chat
  participant LLM as Ollama Llama 3.2
  participant GPT as OpenAI GPT fallback
  participant RAG as RAG Context (pgvector + search)
  participant Vel as GET /api/ai/velocity
  participant Coup as POST /api/ai/coupon-optimize
  participant Bulk as POST /api/coupons/bulk-create
  participant Conv as sahayak_conversations
  participant Audit as audit_logs

  V->>API: Bangla/English intent message
  API->>LLM: Parse intent and tool plan
  alt Ollama unavailable and tier allows fallback
    API->>GPT: Fallback inference
    GPT-->>API: Intent + tool plan
  else Ollama available
    LLM-->>API: Intent + tool plan
  end

  API->>RAG: Retrieve vendor-specific context
  RAG-->>API: Grounding context

  API->>Vel: Fetch slow-moving products
  Vel-->>API: Product velocity set
  API->>Coup: Compute optimized discount options
  Coup-->>API: Discount recommendations

  alt Any tool call fails or times out
    API->>Audit: Log advisory-only fallback due to tool failure
    API->>Conv: Persist partial tool results and failure context
    API-->>V: Partial advisory response\nNo mutation performed
  else Tool calls succeed
    API-->>V: Proposed actions for confirmation

    alt Vendor confirms mutation
      API->>Bulk: Create coupons in bulk
      alt Bulk creation succeeds
        Bulk-->>API: Coupons created
        API->>Audit: Log agent action (mutation)
        API->>Conv: Persist messages + tool_calls + outcome
        API-->>V: Success summary
      else Bulk creation fails
        Bulk-->>API: Error response
        API->>Audit: Log failed mutation attempt
        API->>Conv: Persist partial execution and failure
        API-->>V: Controlled failure with retry options
      end
    else Vendor declines or tool path incomplete
      API->>Audit: Log no-mutation decision
      API->>Conv: Persist advisory-only interaction
      API-->>V: Advisory response without state changes
    end
  end
